Из массива shipmentIds в initVariables верни последний shipment id.
{
  "wf": {
    "initVariables": {
      "shipmentIds": [
        "SHP-01",
        "SHP-02",
        "SHP-03",
        "SHP-04"
      ]
    }
  }
}

Build field latestInvoiceCode from the last element of invoiceCodes.
{
